<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for Holy Saturday</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 15, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Loving God,
</p>

 <p>
Despair or hope?
</p>

 <p>
That was the choice <br></br>
on that day when <br></br>
all seemed lost.
</p>

 <p>
Though it may <br></br>
seem foolish, <br></br>
we choose hope, <br></br>
and wait to see <br></br>
what tomorrow brings.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


